						<p>On a stone set-up at the entrance into the Vīraṭṭānēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Year 16: 987 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>Incomplete. Registers a sale of a garden land called <hi rend="italic">Pāppāṉ tōṭṭam,</hi> out of the <hi rend="italic">mañjikkam</hi> (common property ?) of the <hi rend="italic">ūr</hi> by the <hi rend="italic">sabhā</hi> of Tiruttaṇiyal in Kuṉṟa�kōṭṭam to one Vēḷāṉ Nīlaṉ of Śiṟuvēlūr in Iḷaiyūr-nāḍu, a sub-division of Vēśālippāḍi.</p>						

